  <brief_title>Treatment Of Partial Reversible Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-centre, DB, R and Stratified Parallel Group Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of FP 500mcg Bid vs. SRT 50/250mcg Via Diskus in COPD Pts With Partial Reversible Obstruction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
